<section
    class="relative py-32 md:py-20 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
    style="min-height: 50vh;"
>
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img
            src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dskliu1ig/image/upload/q_auto:best,f_auto/v1769564160/concreto_listo_peru_edqzaq.webp"
            alt="Concreto Listo CONKRET"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center md:object-bottom"
        />
        <!-- Darker Overlay: 60% mobile, 80% desktop -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 md:bg-black/80"></div>
    </div>

    <div
        class="container relative z-10 text-center px-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center"
    >
        <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-6 leading-tight tracking-tight uppercase drop-shadow-lg reveal-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-4"
        >
            ¡Cotiza con los mejores, <br />
            <span class="text-primary" style="color: #e40323 !important;"
                >cotiza con CONKRET!</span
            >
        </h2>
        <p
            class="text-xl text-slate-100 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed drop-shadow-md reveal-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-4"
            data-delay="200"
        >
            Déjanos tus datos y nos comunicaremos contigo en menos de
            <span
                class="text-white font-bold underline decoration-primary decoration-4 underline-offset-8"
                style="text-decoration-color: #e40323 !important;"
                >20 minutos</span
            >. Garantizamos la mejor relación calidad-precio del mercado.
        </p>

        <div
            class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 justify-center items-center w-full reveal-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-4"
            data-delay="400"
        >
            <a
                href="/cotiza/"
                class="btn-cta inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full font-black uppercase tracking-wider transition-all duration-300 group"
                style="padding: 1.25rem 3rem !important;"
            >
                <span>Solicitar Cotización Ahora</span>
                <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="24"
                    height="24"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2.5"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                    ><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"
                    ></path></svg
                >
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .btn-cta {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #e40323, #b3021b);
        color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(228, 3, 35, 0.5);
        text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        display: inline-flex !important;
        height: auto !important;
        line-height: 1.2 !important;
    }
    .btn-cta:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff1f3f, #d60424);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 30px -5px rgba(228, 3, 35, 0.7);
    }
</style>
